                    <span>2011-09-30</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">要读此书~</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="708354859">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-708354859" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-708354859" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="708354859">有用</a>
