  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6507622">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6507622/" class="title-link">粵語書寫</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6507622"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/4472579/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4472579-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4472579/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">沉香</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-01-13"
      class="main-meta">2014-01-13 21:20:10</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6507622_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  粵語是極具寫作潛力的方言，今天在香港仍然非常活躍的粵語寫作，在晚清時已經有值得注意的成就。  语音字典(VoiceDic)是一个用于查询汉字在各种方言中发音的工具，目前已支持汉语方言（普通话、广州话、闽南话、潮州话、苏州话、上海话、客家话、围头话等）、日语汉字等几个语...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6507622_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6507622_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





